Step To deploy 
Go to packege.json > write on top -
 "homepage": "http://birhanu-tech.github.io/netflix-clone-2024",
Then go to secret > write this two above build
"predeploy": "npm run build",
    "deploy": "gh-pages -d dist",
 Then go to push
-Ls
–	 npm i gh-pages --save-dev
-Git add .
                   – git commit –m  deploy
                  – git push
               – npm run deploy
If succesfilly deploy will see Published
